Package: arocAuth
Title: AROC Shiny Application Authentication Module
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("AROC", "Dev", email = "aroc-enquiries@uow.edu.au", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides token-based authentication, hierarchical access resolution,
    and a Shiny module for use across AROC Shiny applications. Supports
    Organisation > Area > Facility hierarchy resolution via vw_orglist,
    multiple UserTypes, and configurable dataset flag filtering.
